006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype;
007
008import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
009
010/**
011 * The common interface for all data type implementations supported by a custom
012 * Java class.
013 *
014 * @param <TYPE>
015 *          the type of the custom Java class
016 */
017public interface ICustomJavaDataType<TYPE extends ICustomJavaDataType<TYPE>> {
018  /**
019   * Provides a copy of the data value associated with the Datatype instance.
020   *
021   * @return the copy
022   */
023  @NonNull
024  TYPE copy();
025}
